Interface BasicLogModel

All Known Subinterfaces:
ILoggerModel
All Known Implementing Classes:
LoggerModel
public interface BasicLogModel
Defines the behavior of a basic logging model for managing log entries of various types. Allows adding, clearing, and retrieving log entries.
